Package eu.liveGov.libraries.livegovtoolkit.activities_fragments

Class Summary
ARFragment This Fragment implements, LBS, IBS, and IBS* AR.
DetailActivity Display details about an item from a list, the map, or from augmented reality fragments.
DetailFragment Fragment to display details about an item clicked from list, map or AR.
ListaFragment Display all items (Urban Plans) in a list.
MapFragment Fragment to show OpenStreet Map with all the items.
QuestionaireFragment Show the questions for an item (Urban Plan)
QuestionaireResultFragment Show the results of the questionnaires in pie charts.
UserInformationActivity Display personal information about the user of the application.
UserInformationFragment Display information about the user in the UserInformationActivity.
UserInformationQuestionaireFragment Display questions inside the UserInformationActivity.
